<p begin="19547200000t" end="19558000000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle461">It's hard.</p>
<p begin="19571600000t" end="19600400000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle462">It's hard for me to get close to Him.</p>
<p begin="19622000000t" end="19640000000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle463">Unlike other people.</p>
<p begin="19640800000t" end="19651600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle464">Unlike you.</p>
<p begin="19652400000t" end="19675200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle465">[Nur breathes shakily]</p>
<p begin="19725600000t" end="19757200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle466">If you want to know, when I was a child,</p>
