<p begin="19864000000t" end="19903600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle469"><span style="style.center_1">I'd listen in at the school windows.</span></p>
<p begin="19907200000t" end="19925200000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle470"><span style="style.center_1">At the mosque's gate.</span></p>
<p begin="19949600000t" end="19997600000t" region="region.after" style="style.center" xml:id="subtitle471"><span style="style.center_1">I couldn't afford to go to school to get</span><br/><span style="style.center_1">a formal education like everyone else.</span></p>
